{"tid":872824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵通車】營運一個月 日均客量僅3.5萬 議員憂大白象越養越肥","createTime":"2018-10-23T03:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T16:49:48.000Z","uid":30647,"like":188,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a4facef12945e6f1a91a4785a703b2edb12ba4","tid":872824,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"【高鐵通車】營運一個月 日均客量僅3.5萬 議員憂大白象越養越肥<br />\n高鐵港段長期被質疑為大白象工程，營運1個月，客量仍然未見起色。港鐵提供截至上周五的最新客量數據，<span style=\"color: red;\">高鐵港段營運27日，總客量為130萬人次，日均接載約5萬客。惟扣除7天內地黃金周檔期後，日均客量不足4萬人次，僅及港府最佳估算一半；<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">近期日均客量更跌至不足3.5萬人次</span></span>。有立法會議員擔心，高鐵客量持續萎靡，隨時要啟動補貼機制，「大白象只會越養越肥」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181023/58821959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181023%2F58821959&d=MxlQAsTwfMfJU6fmmQTBWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=61e84282\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181023%2F58821959&h=ec870c6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181023/58821959</a>"},{"pid":"a12f254ebee0d5610acf137d6e1154a0636b2d06","tid":872824,"uid":52215,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"去遠少少地方，一日得一班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69931f2ee5aae1c2d7d1832af6d814047712fb6","tid":872824,"uid":57513,"like":165,"dislike":0,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"其他人一早估到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fffb6000ad2323eaf2affd9615df3ac897be75","tid":872824,"uid":95,"like":212,"dislike":1,"score":211,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老味近既有直通車，遠既就